{"tid":254807,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【英遇恐襲】IS承認策動襲擊 「在人群中放置炸彈」","createTime":"2017-05-23T12:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T15:51:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"994e387075cb1dac605ea116d2fd7b2dea851b38","tid":254807,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495541807_fdb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495541807_fdb4.jpg&h=a7059949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國小天后Ariana Grande周一晚在英國曼徹斯特體育館（Manchester Arena）舉行演唱會期間發生爆炸，導致22死59傷，「伊斯蘭國」（IS）旗下通訊社阿馬克（Amaq）發聲明承認策動襲擊，「一名哈里發戰士成功在曼徹斯特市十字軍聚會的人群中放置炸彈」。<br />\n<br />\n「伊斯蘭國」聲稱，襲擊造成30名「十字軍」死亡，另外有70人受傷，死傷數字較英國官方公佈的為高。「伊斯蘭國」未有交代行兇者是否已經死亡。<br />\n英國政府將事件列作恐怖襲擊處理，並在現場引爆另一個懷疑炸彈裝置。首相文翠珊讉責襲擊，並向死傷者致哀，更暫停在大選拉票活動。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月，英國倫敦發生恐怖襲擊。一名刀手在倫敦西敏橋駕車撞到多名途人，之後持刀襲擊國會外一名警員，刀手隨後被擊斃，IS其後亦承認責任。"},{"pid":"ac8b152c9d5b07e141553fd99dd3a97b01513392","tid":254807,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:51:31.000Z","msg":"十字軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea36d5e0d7e75b5b5d6b2ef326306ee72bd2f27","tid":254807,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"586a7f78fdeb92d9bd5ed8d047a8e6b8748ff8f4","tid":254807,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf44727bd024b97174558feb3df38525401bdbfb","tid":254807,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢d承認責任，可能根本唔關佢事，但見有野發生就出黎認自己示威</blockquote><br />\n不嬲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/fa